title: Backup QB Power Rankings
itunes:title: Backup QB Power Rankings
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, & Gregg Rosenthal – recap all the latest news from around the NFL including Ryan Tannehill and Forrest Lamp both suffering injuries. The heroes then sort each backup quarterback around the league into four different tiers. The guys wrap the show by debating which current NFL players are on the Hall of Fame bubble.
